Question: Is the silver spoon to the left of the white food?

Reference Answer: No, the spoon is to the right of the soup.

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/2384830.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='food')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='spoon')
IMAGE1=CROP_LEFTOF(image=IMAGE0,box=BOX1)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What color is the spoon?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What color is the food?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == 'silver' and {ANSWER1} == 'white' else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
